channel.title: Can't login
channel.description: MY friend and i have made a server, and my friend has learned how to portforward. now he says the server is having some people log in and stuff, but when i try logging in, it won't let me... :mad: now iv'e tried portforwarding on my router but it still don't work for some reason... please you guys i need serious help, like im the owner (master) and my friends like the other owner (no. 2). Please help me, i beg of you (well not really...) i forgot to mention, i use windows vista :)
